{\ O (spread)}

186
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:04,000
How’s your old man doing, shitstain?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: How's your dad doing?}

187
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:07,000
I haven’t seen him since
his pub went under!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: I haven't seen it since the bar went bust!}

188
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:10,000
He croak or somethin’?
{\ O (spread)}

189
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:13,000
Word’s going around that
yer mum died in the plague!
{\ O (spread)}

190
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:16,000
Shame, she was a real looker!
{\ O (spread)}

191
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:19,000
He should have sold her off
before she kicked the bucket!
{\ O (spread)}

192
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,000
Dio! Can’t you hear me?! Dio!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Can't you hear me?}

193
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,000
What is it, Father?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: What is it, Dad?}

194
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,000
Oh... Do you need your medicine?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: I don't need medicine}

195
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:31,000
Nah, I don’t need that.
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: I have something important to tell you, come here}

196
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,000
C’mere, I gotta tell you something.
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: Dio}

197
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:35,000
I haven’t got much longer. I know it.
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: I've known for a long time}

198
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:38,000
I’m worried that after I die...
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Memories after I die}

199
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:41,000
My only child will be all by
himself. In that case... Dio,
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: It's all about you, my only son.}

200
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,000
Oi!
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: So}

201
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:45,000
Dio!
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: This, this, accept}

202
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,000
Take this.
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: Give}

203
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:52,000
“Joestar”?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Joestar}

204
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:54,000
He’s a noble.
{\ O (spread)}

205
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,000
And he owes me one.
{\ O (spread)}

206
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,000
When I die, send him that letter.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: When I die, send that letter.}

207
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:02,000
Go to him.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Go to that guy}

208
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:04,500
He’ll take care of you, you can
go to school. Sounds good, don’t it?
{\ O (spread)}

209
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:07,000
Oh! Make sure you put a stamp on it!
{\ O (spread)}

210
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,500
Father...
{\ O (spread)}

211
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:14,000
<i>Now</i> you start acting like a parent?!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Are you acting like a father now?}

212
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,000
You’re a smart boy.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: You are smart.}

213
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:25,125
Don’t lose to anyone! Become
the richest man in the world!
{\ O (spread)}

214
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:24,000
Dio!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Dio}

215
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:15,999
Listen up...
{\ O (spread)}

216
00:13:25,125 --> 00:13:32,250
<i>How’s it going, I ask myself</i>
{\ O (spread)}

217
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:39,375
<i>They keep taking from me,
and it’s driving me mad</i>
{\ O (spread)}

218
00:13:39,375 --> 00:13:46,500
<i>This place reeks of all these deadbeats</i>
{\ O (spread)}

219
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:53,625
<i>I might already be in hell,
the way it makes me sick</i>
{\ O (spread)}

220
00:13:53,625 --> 00:14:00,750
<i>And yet, my mum told me to be noble</i>
{\ O (spread)}

221
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:07,875
<i>She held me and taught me to be proud</i>
{\ O (spread)}

222
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:19,000
<i>“Hey Dio, look up at the stars”</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Look up at the stars}

223
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:23,666
<i>She kept on saying that,
until the illness took her</i>
{\ O (spread)}

224
00:14:23,666 --> 00:14:28,333
Just like that...
{\ O (spread)}

225
00:14:28,333 --> 00:14:33,000
<i>Why are my hands always empty?</i>
{\ O (spread)}

226
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:37,666
<i>Am I just here to be taken from?</i>
{\ O (spread)}

227
00:14:37,666 --> 00:14:42,333
<i>Tell me, Joestar, the sky
that you have over you</i>
{\ O (spread)}

228
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:52,000
<i>Is it blue?</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Is that sky blue?}

229
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:58,500
<i>Tell me, Joestar</i>
{\ O (spread)}

230
00:14:58,500 --> 00:15:05,000
<i>This disgraceful father of
mine, the lowest of the low</i>
{\ O (spread)}

231
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:11,500
<i>A deadbeat will always be a deadbeat</i>
{\ O (spread)}

232
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:29,000
<i>Under this murky sky,</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Under this murky sky, I continued to struggle and die}

233
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:32,250
<i>He struggled and struggled,
and this is how he’s gonna die</i>
{\ O (spread)}

234
00:15:32,250 --> 00:15:35,500
<i>Now, I’ll go take this “inheritance”</i>
{\ O (spread)}

235
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:38,750
<i>I’ll use any means, yes,
to set me on my path</i>
{\ O (spread)}

236
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:56,000
<i>I may have nothing in my hands yet,</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: I still have nothing in my hands, so let's start from here}

237
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:59,750
<i>That means I’ll start from here</i>
{\ O (spread)}

238
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:03,500
<i>Tell me, Joestar, in the sky over you,</i>
{\ O (spread)}

239
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:07,250
<i>Is the sun shining?</i>
{\ O (spread)}

240
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:17,000
<i>It is, isn’t it, Joestar?</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: That's right, Joestar}

241
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:21,600
Oh yeah!
{\ O (spread)}

242
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:26,200
You’ve got something good today too, eh?
{\ O (spread)}

243
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:30,800
Give it back!
{\ O (spread)}

244
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:35,400
Over here!
{\ O (spread)}

245
00:16:35,400 --> 00:16:40,000
Hey Erina, I heard that
your old man’s a quack!
{\ O (spread)}

246
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:44,600
My father’s a real doctor!
{\ O (spread)}

247
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:49,200
Oh really? This hat looks expensive!
{\ O (spread)}

248
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:53,800
Stop it! It was a birthday
present from my mother!
{\ O (spread)}

249
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:58,400
Stop right there!
{\ O (spread)}

250
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:05,000
What are you doing?! Take this!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: What are you doing?}

251
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:09,000
I hate when guys try to
act cool in front of girls!
{\ O (spread)}

252
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:13,000
Ow! That hurt!
{\ O (spread)}

253
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:19,000
-Hey, do you know who this guy is?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Hey, do you know who this is?}

254
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:32,000
If he’s that Jonathan kid
from the Joestar family,
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: After all, this guy is Jona of the Joestar family.}

255
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:34,625
I’m gonna give him even
more of a walloping!
{\ O (spread)}

256
00:17:34,625 --> 00:17:37,250
Ah-ha!
{\ O (spread)}

257
00:17:37,250 --> 00:17:39,875
He <i>is</i> the Joestars’ Jonathan!
{\ O (spread)}

258
00:17:39,875 --> 00:17:42,500
Snotty little rich boy! You think
you’re so high and mighty?
{\ O (spread)}

259
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:45,125
Danny!
{\ O (spread)}

260
00:17:45,125 --> 00:17:47,750
Eh?!
{\ O (spread)}

261
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:50,375
Let’s go already! Shit!
{\ O (spread)}

262
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:55,000
Uh... Are you alright?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Um, are you okay?}

263
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:56,000
Leave me alone!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Leave me alone}

264
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,000
But...
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: but}

265
00:17:57,000 --> 00:18:01,000
I did this because I wanted to.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: I did it because I wanted to, not to be thanked by you.}

266
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:06,714
I didn’t do it to get you to thank me.
{\ O (spread)}

267
00:18:06,714 --> 00:18:12,428
My goal is to become a true gentleman.
{\ O (spread)}

268
00:18:12,428 --> 00:18:18,142
You were a damsel in distress,
so I had to stand up for you.
{\ O (spread)}

269
00:18:18,142 --> 00:18:23,857
I’ll beat them, someday.
{\ O (spread)}

270
00:18:23,857 --> 00:18:29,571
Let’s go, Danny!
{\ O (spread)}

271
00:18:29,571 --> 00:18:35,285
Oh, wait!
{\ O (spread)}

272
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:43,000
Jonathan Joestar...
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Jonathan Joestar}

273
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,000
You...
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: you}

274
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:12,000
You must be Dio Brando!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: You're Dio Brando!}

275
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:11,999
And you’re...
{\ O (spread)}

276
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:16,000
Jonathan Joestar?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: So you're Jonathan Joestar?}

277
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:18,000
Everyone calls me JoJo. Nice to meet you!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Everyone calls me Chocho!}

278
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:20,500
Ah, Danny! I’ll introduce you.
{\ O (spread)}

279
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:23,000
This is my friend, Danny.
He’s a clever old hound!
{\ O (spread)}

280
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:25,500
Oh, and don’t worry about him biting!
{\ O (spread)}

281
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,000
Friend?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: friend?}

282
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:30,666
Yeah!
{\ O (spread)}

283
00:19:30,666 --> 00:19:31,333
Danny! What was that for!
{\ O (spread)}

284
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:34,000
Danny!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Danny!}

285
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:39,000
You won’t get away with this!
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: What are you doing? I won't forgive you!}

286
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:42,000
We’ve been waiting for you, Dio Brando.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: I've been waiting for you, Diobrando.}

287
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,000
Lord Joestar!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Lord Joestar!}

288
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:47,400
Come inside!
{\ O (spread)}

289
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:49,800
From today on, you’ll be
living here in our mansion.
{\ O (spread)}

290
00:19:49,800 --> 00:19:52,200
Something wrong, JoJo?
{\ O (spread)}

291
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:54,600
Ah, nothing.
{\ O (spread)}

292
00:19:57,000 --> 00:20:00,000
You’ve travelled all the way from
London, Dio. You must be tired.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: You must be tired from traveling all the way from London, Dio.}

293
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,940
Starting today, you are part of our family.
{\ O (spread)}

294
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:03,880
You’ll be given the same
kind of life as my son, JoJo.
{\ O (spread)}

295
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:05,820
Yes!
{\ O (spread)}

296
00:20:07,760 --> 00:20:11,000
I am grateful for your
kindness, Lord Joestar.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Yes, I am grateful for Lord Joestar's actions.}

297
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,540
Mister Brando!
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: Hehehehe.}

298
00:20:12,540 --> 00:20:16,540
I’m Police Inspector Archer!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Brand, this is Inspector Archer.}

299
00:20:16,540 --> 00:20:18,760
Police? Has something happened?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Police? Did something happen?}

300
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:21,105
Oh, no!
{\ O (spread)}

301
00:20:21,105 --> 00:20:23,450
I’m an old friend of the Joestars.
{\ O (spread)}

302
00:20:23,450 --> 00:20:25,795
Although, I could hear Danny
whimper a moment ago...
{\ O (spread)}

303
00:20:25,795 --> 00:20:28,139
Ah, that was—
{\ O (spread)}

304
00:20:28,139 --> 00:20:30,485
-He came at me so suddenly.
{\ O (spread)}

305
00:20:30,485 --> 00:20:32,830
When I jumped in surprise,
I think my leg may have hit him!
{\ O (spread)}

306
00:20:32,830 --> 00:20:35,175
Danny is the Joestar household’s
wonderful guard dog.
{\ O (spread)}

307
00:20:37,520 --> 00:20:43,760
He’s a friendly creature, but
I’m sorry he surprised you.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: He's quite friendly, but it seems he startled you.}

308
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:45,506
JoJo!
{\ O (spread)}

309
00:20:45,506 --> 00:20:47,253
You’ll let this Danny matter go, right?
{\ O (spread)}

310
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,360
Yes, sir.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: yes.}

311
00:20:51,360 --> 00:20:51,359
Good.
{\ O (spread)}

312
00:20:51,360 --> 00:20:56,320
JoJo has lost his mother too—
and you both are the same age!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Jojo has also lost his mother, and they are the same age.}

313
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:59,300
Make sure to get along with each other.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Please get along well with each other.}

314
00:20:59,300 --> 00:21:02,320
Now, allow me to show you to your room.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Now, let me show you to your room.}

315
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:05,240
Mister Brando!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Mr. Brand.}

316
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:09,160
Nice to have met you!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: nice to meet you!}

317
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:26,120
Don’t touch my bag!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Don't touch my bag.}

318
00:21:26,120 --> 00:21:27,420
I was just trying to carry it for—
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: I'll try to carry it}

319
00:21:27,420 --> 00:21:28,120
That’s enough.
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: 結構}

320
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:32,020
Your hand is covered in dog drool.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Your hands are sticky with dog drool}

321
00:21:32,020 --> 00:21:35,180
Pardon me if I don’t want
it all over my things!
{\ O (spread)}

322
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:38,340
Alright JoJo, I’ll tell
you from the get-go.
{\ O (spread)}

323
00:21:38,120 --> 00:21:39,420
Ta-ta, JoJo!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Listen, JoJo}

324
00:21:38,340 --> 00:21:41,500
I like being the best!
I’m always number one!
{\ O (spread)}

325
00:21:39,420 --> 00:21:24,399
Now then, let me get—
{\ O (spread)}

326
00:21:39,423 --> 00:21:24,399
Watch it!
{\ O (spread)}

327
00:21:41,500 --> 00:21:44,659
I don’t care who you are,
no one looks down on me!
{\ O (spread)}

328
00:21:47,820 --> 00:21:49,820
I was only trying to be friendly!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: I just try to be friendly}

329
00:21:50,020 --> 00:21:52,320
What are you two doing?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: What are you both doing?}

330
00:21:57,120 --> 00:21:58,120
And one more thing—
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: One more thing}

331
00:22:00,120 --> 00:22:02,120
I hate dogs.
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: I hate dogs}

332
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:10,919
The way they grovel and suck
up to humans disgusts me.
{\ O (spread)}

333
00:22:10,919 --> 00:22:19,719
Keep your stupid dog away from me!
{\ O (spread)}

334
00:22:19,719 --> 00:22:28,520
Coming, Lord Joestar!
{\ O (spread)}

335
00:22:28,520 --> 00:22:37,320
Thus, with this meeting, the
two boys’ youth had begun.
{\ O (spread)}

336
00:22:46,120 --> 00:22:47,120
Are you coming, JoJo, Dio?
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Here comes JoJo}

337
00:22:47,120 --> 00:22:50,495
<i>Bear in mind, as honourable nobles,</i>
{\ O (spread)}

338
00:22:50,495 --> 00:22:53,870
<i>We take on the duty of
becoming true gentlemen</i>
{\ O (spread)}

339
00:22:53,870 --> 00:22:57,245
<i>This is why we study, acquire knowledge,</i>
{\ O (spread)}

340
00:22:57,245 --> 00:23:00,620
{\an8}<i>(Without pause!)</i>
{\ O (spread)}

341
00:23:00,620 --> 00:23:03,995
{\an8}<i>(Without limit!)</i>
{\ O (spread)}

342
00:23:03,995 --> 00:23:07,370
<i>And arm ourselves with logic!</i>
{\ O (spread)}

343
00:23:07,370 --> 00:23:10,745
{\an8}<i>(So you’ll never lose!)</i>
{\ O (spread)}

344
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:16,120
<i>Under the guidance of
the goddess of familial love</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Under the Goddess of Self-Love}

345
00:23:16,120 --> 00:23:18,919
<i>For the sake of heading
the house of Joestar</i>
{\ O (spread)}

346
00:23:18,919 --> 00:23:21,719
{\an8}<i>(The honourable Joestars!)</i>
{\ O (spread)}

347
00:23:21,719 --> 00:23:24,520
<i>What’s this, JoJo? JoJo!</i>
{\ O (spread)}

348
00:23:24,520 --> 00:23:27,320
<i>The same mistakes once again</i>
{\ O (spread)}

349
00:23:30,120 --> 00:23:31,120
<i>How many times have
you made them! Six times!</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: How many times has this happened?}

350
00:23:34,120 --> 00:23:38,120
<i>Dio has all of them correct!</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: All uses are correct}

351
00:23:38,120 --> 00:23:46,120
It’s just because I love reading so much!
{\ O (spread)}

352
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:54,120
But they haven’t even
taught us this in school yet!
{\ O (spread)}

353
00:23:54,120 --> 00:24:02,120
<i>Bear in mind, as proud nobles,</i>
{\ O (spread)}

354
00:24:02,120 --> 00:24:10,120
<i>We behave like true gentlemen</i>
{\ O (spread)}

355
00:24:10,120 --> 00:24:18,120
<i>Sit up straight, use your knife with grace,</i>
{\ O (spread)}

356
00:24:16,120 --> 00:24:18,120
<i>Under the guidance of
the goddess of familial love</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Under the Goddess of Self-Love}

357
00:24:18,120 --> 00:24:21,620
<i>For the sake of being loved as a Joestar!</i>
{\ O (spread)}

358
00:24:18,120 --> 00:24:26,120
{\an8}<i>(So elegantly!)</i>
{\ O (spread)}

359
00:24:21,620 --> 00:24:25,120
{\an8}<i>(The proud Joestars!)</i>
{\ O (spread)}

360
00:24:25,120 --> 00:24:28,620
<i>What’s this, JoJo? JoJo!</i>
{\ O (spread)}

361
00:24:28,620 --> 00:24:32,120
<i>Do you call yourself a gentleman?</i>
{\ O (spread)}

362
00:24:32,120 --> 00:24:35,620
<i>Look at Dio’s elegant touch</i>
{\ O (spread)}

363
00:24:34,120 --> 00:24:35,120
{\an8}<i>(So gracefully!)</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: graceful}

364
00:24:35,120 --> 00:24:16,119
<i>So that your mouth always remains spotless</i>
{\ O (spread)}

365
00:24:35,123 --> 00:24:16,119
{\an8}<i>(Unfailingly!)</i>
{\ O (spread)}

366
00:24:35,620 --> 00:24:39,120
<i>His manners are perfect!</i>
