{\ T: I think of those words that have become familiar to me}

795
00:53:38,400 --> 00:53:45,400
<i>Seven years spent studying diligently</i>
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: Seven Years of Prefectural Production}

796
00:53:45,400 --> 00:53:52,400
<i>You’re... beautiful,
