{\ T: You were beautiful and sincere}

797
00:53:52,400 --> 00:53:59,400
<i>My friend, who’s always
pushing me to be better</i>
{\ O (gap)}
{\ T: I straighten my collar, thinking of my friend}

798
00:53:59,400 --> 00:54:06,400
<i>You’ve repented for the
wrong you did to Erina</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: You regretted your mistake of not wearing your collar.}

799
00:54:06,400 --> 00:54:13,900
<i>You’ve offered me a shoulder
to lean on, now that Danny’s gone</i>
{\ O (spread)}

800
00:54:21,400 --> 00:54:26,400
<i>We walked this path
together for seven years</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: We walked together for seven years}

801
00:54:26,400 --> 00:54:26,399
<i>I always followed in your
footsteps, one step behind,</i>
{\ O (spread)}

802
00:54:26,400 --> 00:54:37,400
<i>So why is it that I don’t
