828
00:56:17,500 --> 00:56:19,833
I give in.
{\ O (spread)}

829
00:56:19,833 --> 00:56:22,166
The shaky hands and chest pain,
they’ll likely get better before long.
{\ O (spread)}

830
00:56:22,166 --> 00:56:24,500
Enough of that. You two...
Congratulations on your victory!
{\ O (spread)}

831
00:56:24,500 --> 00:56:26,833
What?!
{\ O (spread)}

832
00:56:26,833 --> 00:56:29,166
What?!
{\ O (spread)}

833
