{\ T: I have endured}

878
00:59:41,500 --> 00:59:44,500
<i>Yes, until the day finally came</i>
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: Yes, until that day}

879
00:59:44,500 --> 00:59:47,866
Bloody hell! Ever since that wench
died I’ve been crumbling in debt!
{\ O (spread)}

880
00:59:47,866 --> 00:59:51,233
I know!
{\ O (spread)}

881
00:59:51,233 --> 00:59:54,600
You pawn this crap and bring
me back some booze instead!
{\ O (spread)}

882
00:59:54,600 --> 00:59:57,966
<i>My one and only memento of mum</i>
{\ O (spread)}

883
00:59:57,966 --> 01:00:01,333
<i>You threw it away!
