{\ O (spread)}

884
01:00:04,700 --> 01:00:06,000
I don’t bloody need it anymore!
{\ O (rank)}
{\ T: I don't need it anymore}

885
01:00:06,000 --> 01:00:08,250
<i>He’s the one who killed mum</i>
{\ O (spread)}

886
01:00:08,250 --> 01:00:10,500
<i>Everything’s been
