896
01:00:58,000 --> 01:01:03,000
<i>A world where everything is perfect,</i>
{\ O (spread)}

897
01:01:03,000 --> 01:01:08,000
<i>In the palm of your hand, Dio!</i>
{\ O (spread)}

898
01:01:08,000 --> 01:01:13,000
Dio!
{\ O (spread)}

899
01:01:13,000 --> 01:01:18,000
What’s that in your hand? Medicine?
