03:10:52,833 --> 03:10:55,666
-I’m worried, so please do the speech instead!
{\ O (spread)}

2609
03:10:55,666 --> 03:10:58,500
-He’s—that’s in the past.
{\ O (spread)}

2610
03:10:58,500 --> 03:11:01,333
