{\ O (spread)}

2611
03:11:01,333 --> 03:11:04,166
I wanted to voice some
personal thoughts here.
{\ O (spread)}

2612
03:11:04,166 --> 03:11:07,000
First off, as Mr. Hirose said before,
{\ O (spread)}

2613
03:11:07,000 --> 03:11:09,833
It’s been a long road to
arrive at our final performance.
{\ O (spread)}

2614
03:11:09,833 --> 03:11:12,666
And I’m relieved that we made it.
{\ O (spread)}

2615
03:11:12,666 --> 03:11:15,500
Truly, I’m truly happy to
be on this stage. Thank you!
{\ O (spread)}

2616
03:11:15,500 --> 03:11:18,333
